snippet.title: Ski Play - V.0.3.0 -  Alpha III (gameplay from SDK no sound)
snippet.description:
Major new update that make playable the game on the SDK
Reprogramming the engine of the scrolling and solve other bug

Come try the game on https://samplay.itch.io/ski-play

You can get your own opponent NFT on https://opensea.io/collection/ski-play
